* Are a Bachelor or Master student in the direction Business Administration, Industrial Engineering and Management, Data analytics or AI;
* Have knowledge about artificial intelligence engines;
* Have knowledge of applications and the ability to apply on large data sets;
* Are a proactive person with a can\-do mindset;
* Have strong stakeholder management skills;

